  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "According to https://github.com/ethereum/wiki/wiki/JSON-RPC, quantities should be hex encoded with the 0x prefix but no leading zeroes (i.e. 0x400 instead of 0x0400), but geth accepts both forms.\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\n```\r\n$ curl -X POST --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"eth_getBlockByNumber\",\"params\":[\"0x01b4\", true],\"id\":1}' http://localhost:8545\r\n{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":1,\"result\":{\"difficulty\":\"0xe1bd4\",\"extraData\":\"0xd783010502846765746887676f312e362e33856c696e7578\",\"gasLimit\":\"0xa739b8\",\"gasUsed\":\"0x0\",\"hash\":\"0x4a89e885e0a6cc17b78d790320833299b550d47c36287b0d8d4fda97684a777a\",\"logsBloom\":\"\",\"miner\":\"0xc2fa6dcef5a1fbf70028c5636e7f64cd46e7cfd4\",\"mixHash\":\"0x9ea5c067c1c19a170b349ae3c9f41285fb2c0a7cef92b117f25ed7ca6da86314\",\"nonce\":\"0x6188497bd6f143d9\",\"number\":\"0x1b4\",\"parentHash\":\"0x3a2e26193bf74178717951b6696e937607b62615bbf91dd6ae192001006bdb4a\",\"receiptsRoot\":\"0x56e81f171bcc55a6ff8345e692c0f86e5b48e01b996cadc001622fb5e363b421\",\"sha3Uncles\":\"0x1dcc4de8dec75d7aab85b567b6ccd41ad312451b948a7413f0a142fd40d49347\",\"size\":\"0x219\",\"stateRoot\":\"0xba9f4d1af1371ab66551526776697af24d9df3492ac67bec3b913534fe85d95a\",\"timestamp\":\"0x5831c32b\",\"totalDifficulty\":\"0x16ae78d0\",\"transactions\":[],\"transactionsRoot\":\"0x56e81f171bcc55a6ff8345e692c0f86e5b48e01b996cadc001622fb5e363b421\",\"uncles\":[]}}\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: 1.6.0-unstable\r\nOS & Version: Linux Ubuntu 16.10\r\nCommit hash : 49437a02c981199c62048fae00c6b80976f6e6b9\r\n",
